<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>PowerSprout Home</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
</head>
<body class="home-body">
  <header class="main-header">
    <a href="/" class="logo-link">
      <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="PowerSprout Logo" class="navbar-logo" />
    </a>
    <nav class="nav-links">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a>
      <a href="#about">About</a>
    </nav>
    <img src="/images/menu.png" alt="Menu Icon" class="menu-icon" id="menuToggle" />
  </header>

  <!-- Slide-in Menu -->
  <div class="slide-menu" id="slideMenu">
    <div class="slide-menu-content">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a>
      <a href="/#about">About</a>
      <a href="/vision">Vision</a>
      <a href="/mission">Mission</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="scroll-section">

    <!-- Problem Statement Overlay -->
    <div class="overlay-block">
      <h1 class="scroll-heading">Problem Statement</h1>
      <div class="content-row">
        <div class="content-text">
          <p>
            The UAE generates over 3.27 million tonnes of food waste annually—translating into a staggering $3.5 billion in losses. When dumped into landfills, this waste anaerobically decomposes, releasing methane, a gas 25x more potent than CO₂, accelerating climate change.
            <br><br>
            Despite the UAE’s progressive smart city goals, real-time, IoT-enabled bioconversion technologies like Microbial Fuel Cells (MFCs) remain largely untapped. This creates a critical gap in sustainable energy innovation from organic waste at scale.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="content-image">
          <img src="images/3.27 million waste.png" alt="Food Waste Problem" class="section-image" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Vision Overlay -->
    <div class="overlay-block">
      <h1 class="scroll-heading">Our Vision</h1>
        <div class="content-overlay">
          <div class="content-row">
            <div class="content-text">
              <p>
                To revolutionize how the world sees food waste—not as garbage, but as a renewable energy resource. At PowerSprout, we envision a future where food scraps fuel clean electricity through smart Microbial Fuel Cells, monitored by scalable IoT systems.
                <br><br>
                Our mission is to power entire campuses, communities, and eventually cities—starting in the UAE—by transforming bulk food waste into storable, sensor-driven energy. We aim to lead the shift toward sustainable, carbon-conscious living, one waste-powered system at a time.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="content-image">
              <img src="images/vision_picture.png" alt="Our Vision" class="section-image" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>

  </section>

  <script>
    const menuIcon = document.getElementById('menuToggle');
    const slideMenu = document.getElementById('slideMenu');

    menuIcon.addEventListener('click', () => {
      slideMenu.classList.toggle('show');
    });

    slideMenu.querySelectorAll('a').forEach(link => {
      link.addEventListener('click', () => {
        slideMenu.classList.remove('show');
      });
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
